name: Daren_(Yavin_4)
content:
Daren was a Human male smuggler who operated on Yavin 4 near the Massassi Temple during the Galactic Civil War.
Daren was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Daren was added to the game along with the smuggling missions introduced with the "Chapter 3" update, released on September 27, 2006.
